    "description": "Mirai Works Inc. engages in the human recruitment and procurement support in Japan. The company offers FreeConsultant.jp, a freelance matching service; Skill Shift, a local side job matching service; MOREWORKS, a creator matching service; ConsulNext.jp, a consulting job changes support service; and Glocal Mission Jobs, a local job changes support services. It also provides consulting services for large companies; Re-skilling, a practical reskilling service for corporate human resources; Booster, an open innovation platform for pre-seed and seed startups, local governments, and business companies; regional revitalization project, a support services for local governments; and sustainability management support business for companies and local governments, as well as operating media outlet, such as MWRI, Career Knock, Uragawa, Glocal Mission Times, and Green Note. Mirai Works Inc. was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
